      <title>Verizon 報告稱，由於靈活的計劃需求，季度用戶流失減少</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/verizon-posts-fewer-first-quarter-subscriber-losses-flexible-plan-demand-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Verizon Communications 週一表示，由於其靈活的計劃和為 Netflix 和華納兄弟 Discovery 的 Max 等服務提供折扣價格的串流媒體捆綁服務，該公司第一季無線用戶流失數量低於預期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/verizon-posts-fewer-first-quarter-subscriber-losses-flexible-plan-demand-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 11:07:37 GMT</pubDate>
